rows.label: qst103307_msg0002
rows.name:
S-sorry... This is the first time
I've dealt with a case like this...

rows.label: qst103307_msg0003
rows.name:
Thank you! Were my siblings
well? Were they lonely?

rows.label: qst103307_msg0005
rows.name:
If only Dad would come back, their
lives would be much easier...

rows.label: qst103307_msg0006
rows.name:
After Mom passed away, he left,
saying "Blame the Empire"...

rows.label: qst103307_msg0007
rows.name:
And now, thanks to the Empire,
our family can eat...

rows.label: qst103307_msg0008
rows.name: Never mind my story, it's the case!

rows.label: qst103307_msg0009
rows.name:
The deceased is a woman, but
we don't have any clues...

rows.label: qst103307_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm sorry... I hope we can
find a lead to solve this.
